  "description": "A single gentle fold in warm paper. foldAmt at 0.08 — the waveform barely bends, no harmonic spray, no aggression. One layer, near-perfect symmetry at 0.98. The filter sits warm at 0.45 cutoff, soft and unhurried. Long attack (0.5s) and slow release (2.8s) let the note breathe like a held sheet slowly lowered to a table. Origami in repose.",
